Package: pinfo201
Type: Package
Title: Practice coding for INFO 201, Foundation Skills for Data Science
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Hendry
Maintainer: David Hendry <dhendry@uw.edu>
Description: This package enables instructors to create practice sets for learning to code in R. In addition to giving beginner coders coding tasks and feedback, this package provides functions for automatically grading student work.
    This package installs an Addin menu into RStudio, which is intended for learners. Instructions are given a set of admin functions for working with instruction sets.  
    Instruction sets are specified with a small number of package-specific tags, which are wrapped around R code.
